    • visitCode

      @Nullable public @Nullable ExprVisitor visitCode(byte @NotNull [] locals)
      Description copied from class: CodesVisitor
      Visit the code of a function.

      This completes the locals and body fields of a function whose type was visited in FunctionsVisitor.visitFunc(int)

      Each call to this function should match a FunctionsVisitor.visitFunc(int) call to the corresponding FunctionsVisitor obtained from ModuleVisitor.visitFuncs(), if it was not null.

      Overrides:
      visitCode in class CodesVisitor
      Parameters:
      locals - The valtypes of the local variables of the function.
      Returns:
      An ExprVisitor to visit with the body of the function, or null if this visitor is not interested in the body of the function.
